<plot>Kate is stuck in an abusive relationship with Johnny who is a security guard at their local bank but he is a gambler who drinks away his pay check every week. After the bank threatens to repossess their home Kate decides she must deal with this for the welfare of her baby so she robs the bank dressed as a man. The teller slips a dye bomb in one of the bags staining all the bills. Kate takes Johnnys money out of his wallet &amp; replaces it with the stained money. After depositing the good money back into the bank Kate waits for Johnny to arrive. Minutes later the police enter the bank &amp; drag a protesting Johnny to their car. Kate is free of Johnny &amp; has the money for a better life for both of them.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?183997</url></doc>
